Mercent Announces E-Commerce Partnership and Platform Integration With eBay Inc's eBay Enterprise
Monday, 23 Sep 2013 08:14pm EDT
Mercent, a technology company that enables retailers to profitably reach and convert more shoppers online, announced it has signed a strategic partnership with eBay Inc's eBay Enterprise. eBay Enterprise enables omnichannel commerce, multichannel retailing and digital marketing for global enterprises in the U.S. and internationally. Under the terms of the partnership, eBay Enterprise will use Mercent's Mercent Retail SAAS platform to market and sell its clients' full product portfolios across comparison shopping engines and product listing ad programs.Â 
